OL,3,CCouncils 'should have a say' over
OL,4,Cmigrant hotels, Lib Dem leader claims
OL,6,FLocal councils should get a say over
OL,7,Fwhether hotels are used to house
OL,8,Fasylum seekers in their area,
OL,9,Faccording to the leader of the Liberal
OL,10,FDemocrats.
OL,12,FSir Ed Davey told ITV News Meridian
OL,13,Fthe fact councils currently aren't
OL,14,Fgiven any role by the Home Office is
OL,15,Fone of the department's "many
OL,16,Ffailings".
