OL,3,CCouncils 'should have a say' over
OL,4,Cmigrant hotels, Lib Dem leader claims
OL,6,FThe Lib Dem conference is taking place
OL,7,Fin Bournemouth, where there have been
OL,8,Fregular protests over recent months in
OL,9,Fresponse to three local hotels being
OL,10,Fused to house asylum seekers on behalf
OL,11,Fof the government.
OL,13,FThe party has set out proposals to
OL,14,Fclose asylum hotels within six months
OL,15,Fof winning power by setting up
OL,16,Femergency processing centres modelled
OL,17,Fon the Nightingale hospitals used
OL,18,Fduring the Covid-19 pandemic.
