OL,3,CCouncils 'should have a say' over
OL,4,Cmigrant hotels, Lib Dem leader claims
OL,6,FAsked if councils should have a role
OL,7,Fin approving migrant hotels, Sir Ed
OL,8,Fsaid: "Well, they should. The problem
OL,9,Fis the Home Office doesn't do its job
OL,10,Fproperly. That's why Liberal Democrats
OL,11,Fare saying: Home Office do your job
OL,12,Fproperly.
OL,14,F"There should be an emergency called.
OL,15,FWe should get the resources in. We're
OL,16,Fthe only party putting forward a
OL,17,Fpractical policy to get down the
OL,18,Fasylum backlog created by the
OL,19,FConservatives and deport the people
OL,20,Fwho shouldn't be here.
