OL,3,CCouncils 'should have a say' over
OL,4,Cmigrant hotels, Lib Dem leader claims
OL,6,F"But unlike some others, we're saying
OL,7,Fthat if people have a right to be
OL,8,Fhere, genuine refugees, we should take
OL,9,Fthem and they should be able to get on
OL,10,Fwith their lives."
OL,12,FThe Bournemouth conference has also
OL,13,Ffocussed on "reclaiming the flag" from
OL,14,Fright-wing parties such as Reform UK.
OL,16,FA crowd of Lib Dem activists waving
OL,17,FUnion flags welcomed Sir Ed to the
OL,18,Fconference, as he led a marching band
OL,19,Fthrough Bournemouth Central Gardens.
