OL,3,CCouncils 'should have a say' over
OL,4,Cmigrant hotels, Lib Dem leader claims
OL,6,FSir Ed said: "Let's claim the flag
OL,7,Fback for the decent people in Britain
OL,8,Fwho yes, they want things like
OL,9,Fimmigration and asylum problems
OL,10,Fsolved, but they also want the
OL,11,Fproblems in the health service solved."
OL,13,FOfficial figures show there were more
OL,14,Fthan 32,000 asylum seekers housed in
OL,15,FUK hotels at the end of June 2025.
